Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.21,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,901.334)}- Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.58,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yama-chan got it right just now
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:16.05,Hamada,,0,0,0,,But I 100% saw him peeking at this cardboard
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:16.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,901.334)}- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:18.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,That's what we said!\N- Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\pos(1239,930)\3c&H1738E7&}The proof
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the proof Hosei cheated
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:29.98,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Get ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:32.62,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Punishment game for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:38.21,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Please, wait... he kept on flipping that thing so I could see it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.78,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,- Punishment time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:42.18,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to see it, but I couldn't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:45.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,He kept on flipping that thing on my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:47.82,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Nope, you're out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.42,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:52.62,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Can't blame him
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:54.39,Endo,,0,0,0,,Be brave, Hosei
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:57.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,What should I do now, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724,904.667)}Just tell me!\N{\rMatsumoto}- Principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:59.43,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Alright, so...\N{\rDefault2}- Spare me, principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,250)\bord4\fs100\pos(744,706)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H2340D8&\t(0,0,\fs120}Don't ever stop! The no-stop club!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.10,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ready for the usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.22,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:08.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,I saw that before
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:09.94,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's all you ever do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,He's holding a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:11.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(702,912.667)}You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:12.76,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's his baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:15.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Come on, switch into something else!\N{\rEndo}- Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.28,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,He's born
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,Congratulations for your newborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.45,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's what you get
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:25.62,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Cheating is the thing our principal hates the most
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.62,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,912.667)}Yeah, that's no good
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,Here comes\N{\rMatsumoto}- Maybe he'll come up with something new
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:31.13,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.43,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I can see a change!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:36.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's the Moustache-dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,912.667)}A new trend?
