Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:43.31,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Don't you think he just entered eco-mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:43.31,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,912.667)}I do {\rMatsumoto}      - Sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:49.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is the most basic type
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.98,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's thinking about the next move
