Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:01.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's Ei-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:02.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,912.667)}It's Eikichi Yazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.64,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:06.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,So cool, such a cool face
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:07.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's Ei-chan
