Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.46,0:22:26.76,Hosei,,0,0,0,,So, it's summer now\N{\rTanaka}- Right, we're in the middle of the summer break
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:31.17,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,How do you plan on spending it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:31.17,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724,904.667)}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:32.23,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.23,0:22:34.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Are you going somewhere with your families?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:36.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I'm not\N{\rHosei} - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:38.77,Hamada,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's gonna be crowded wherever we'd go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:41.11,Hosei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(729,908)}I'm going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:42.38,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:43.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:45.98,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's pretty standard\N{\rHamada}- Just go, who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:48.55,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I will\N{\rEndo}- If you'll have time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:50.22,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Of course, if I can
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:52.64,Hosei,,0,0,0,,And I also wanna do that, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.52,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I wanna do that rocket thing\N{\rTanaka}- Ah, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:55.46,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That one!\N{\rTanaka}- Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.46,0:22:59.26,Hosei,,0,0,0,,You put it on your feet and it flies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:01.26,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It uses water pressure to make you float
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.26,0:23:03.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah, the jetpack thingy?\N{\rTanaka}- That one
