Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.10,0:23:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,0)\shad0\3c&HFF201E&\pos(558,816)}Flyboard
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.10,0:23:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,0)\pos(871.5,906)}It uses the power of the water for a jet propulsion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:05.03,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:07.14,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1124,830)}And it sprays water, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:07.14,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's right, it's very powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:09.14,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(770,744.667)}I never actually saw one of those
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.68,0:23:09.14,Endo,,0,0,0,,Me neither
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.14,0:23:11.71,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Isn't there an ad for it?    {\rTanaka} - Yep
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.71,0:23:13.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You wanna do it?{\rHosei}    - I'm doing it in two days
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:16.11,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Are they like boots?           {\rHosei} - That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.11,0:23:20.42,Hosei,,0,0,0,,And from its side it sprays water, it makes you fly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:23.52,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I wanna show it to my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:25.89,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I wanna appeal to them
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:28.69,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Flying like fwaaaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.64,0:23:31.66,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's it\N{\rMatsumoto}- What's so funny about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.78,0:23:34.60,Hosei,,0,0,0,,It's really fun!\N{\rMatsumoto}- Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:36.27,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,By the sea?\N{\rHosei}- Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:37.62,Endo,,0,0,0,,You'll do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.62,0:23:40.40,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.62,0:23:40.40,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Definitely, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:41.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Are they going to film you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:43.74,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Of course\N{\rHamada}- Perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:48.21,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We gotta see it, maybe we'll persuade Hamada into trying it himself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.21,0:23:49.86,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Please, do!
