Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:54.82,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I really want to\N{\rHosei}- I want to see the principal fly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:56.52,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,In Hamada's Cram School?\N{\rHosei}- Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.52,0:23:58.15,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No way he'll do it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.15,0:23:59.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even like to walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:02.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's not true
